<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	<title>olpcMAP: Community-Made Maps</title>
	<link rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' href='http://mapmeld.appspot.com/mapmeldStyles.css'/>
	<script type='text/javascript'>
function shareLink(opt){
	$("subform").style.display="block";
	if(opt==0){
	
	}
	else{
	
	}
}
function contactMode(){
	$("coverwindow").style.display="block";
}
function closeCoverWindow(){
	$("coverwindow").style.display="none";
}
function $(id){return document.getElementById(id);}
	</script>
	<style type='text/css'>
html{width:100%;height:100%;}
body{width:100%;height:100%;margin:0px;padding:0px;background-color:#c9c9ff;}
div.main{
	background-color:silver;
	border-left:1px solid #000000;
	border-right:1px solid #000000;
}
span.navoption a{
	color:#000000;
	text-decoration:none;
}
span.navoption a:hover{
	color:#0000bb;
	text-decoration:underline;
}
span.navoption:hover{
	color:#0000bb;
	text-decoration:underline;
}
a.tab{
	font-size:11pt;
	margin-left:8px;
	margin-right:8px;
	font-weight:normal;
}
a.tab-select{
	text-decoration:none;
	color:#500;
	font-weight:bold;
	margin-left:8px;
	margin-right:8px;
}
h4{
	margin-top:20pt;
}
div.mapdesc{
	min-height:200px;
}
button.submit{
	background: transparent url(http://mapmeld.appspot.com/bg_submit-report.png) repeat-x;
	border: solid #208A08;
	border-bottom: none;
	padding: 9px 12px 9px 12px;
}
	</style>
</head>
<body>
	<div class="header">
		<h3><span style='font-size:1.7em;'>olpcMAP Community</span>- sites and networks based on our map</h3>
		<br/>
	</div>
	<div class="nav" style="border-bottom:1px solid black;">
		<span class="navoption"><a href="http://olpcMAP.net">Map Page</a></span>
		<span class="navoption"><a href="http://wiki.laptop.org/go/OlpcMAP/data-api">Data API</a></span>
		<span class="navoption"><a href="http://wiki.laptop.org/go/OlpcMAP" target="_blank">Wiki</a></span>
		<span class="navoption"><a href="#" onclick="contactMode()">Contact</a></span>
	</div>
	<div class="main">
		<br/><br/>
		<h4>olpcMAP Sprint</h4>
		<div>
			<a href="http://wiki.laptop.org/go/OlpcMAP#Global_MAP_making_SPRINT:_Dec_27-31.2C_2010_in_Boston" target="_blank">
				<img src="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/__rJtABokm_Q/TPmRcFBeGlI/AAAAAAAACwA/xWzdKl0A3-o/s400/olpcmap.png" style="max-width:350px;max-height:200px;float:left;"/>
			</a>
			<div class="mapdesc">
				<p><a href="http://wiki.laptop.org/go/OlpcMAP#Global_MAP_making_SPRINT:_Dec_27-31.2C_2010_in_Boston" target="_blank">olpcMAP Sprint</a> by OLPC</p>
				<p>A community event from Dec 27th-31st happening worldwide and based at OLPC's office in Cambridge.  Closing out 2010 with a new event (modeled after book sprints)
				to map the world of Sugar and OLPC users, and to add meaning to our growing network.</p>
				<p>This event also aims to develop our mapmaking tools so that students, teachers, and activists can share their experiences and connect with the world.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<br/>
		<button class="submit" onclick="shareLink(0);"><span style="color:#ffffff;">Share Map Link</span></button>
		<button class="submit" onclick="shareLink(1);" style="margin-left:25px;"><span style="color:#ffffff;">Share Map Idea</span></button>
		<form id="subform" style="display:none;width:400px;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;padding:7px;border:solid #208A08;background-color:#ffffff;">
			<span style="font-size:14pt;">Sharing a Map</span>
			<hr/>
			Mapname: <input name="mapname" width="350"/><br/>
			Makers: <input name="makers" width="350"/><br/>
			Site Link: <input name="link" width="350"/><br/>
			Concept Link: <input name="concept" width="350"/><br/>
			Description: <textarea name="describe" width="350" height="300"></textarea><br/>
			<input type="submit" value="Send"/>
		</form>
		<br/>
		<h4>OLPC Connections</h4>
		<div>
			<a href="http://www.olpcsouthasia.org/connections/" target="_blank">
				<img src="http://mapmeld.appspot.com/olpcConn.png" style="max-width:350px;max-height:200px;float:left;"/>
			</a>
			<div class="mapdesc">
				<p><a href="http://www.olpcsouthasia.org/connections/" target="_blank">OLPC Connections</a> by Shirish Goyal</p>
				<p>Sections on the right provide features such as Search, Connect to Volunteer, Ideas, My Neighborhood, and Profile of the Day.
				Each point in the map can have a separate profile page to showcase pictures, videos, stories, ideas, and expertise.</p>
				<p>Clustering is present for collections of points within a small region, showing the number of total points in the cluster.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<br/>
		<h4>olpcMAP CrowdMap</h4>
		<div>
			<a href="http://olpcmap.crowdmap.com" target="_blank">
				<img src="http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2010/9/15/1284576720173/Pope-CrowdMap-006.jpg" style="max-width:350px;max-height:200px;float:left;"/>
			</a>
			<div class="mapdesc">
				<p><a href="http://olpcmap.crowdmap.com" target="_blank">Ushahidi Reports</a> by olpcMAPmakers</p>
				<p>Bring volunteers and deployments to the attention of the olpcMAPmakers team by adding reports to this CrowdMap (based on Ushahidi)</p>
				<p>Also acts as a news center for Tweets and blog posts about olpc and #olpcMAP</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<br/>
		<h4>Bing! olpcMAP reloaded</h4>
		<div>
			<a href="http://mapmeld.appspot.com/bingtest.html" target="_blank">
				<img src="http://blogs.msdn.com/blogfiles/keithkin/WindowsLiveWriter/BingMapsForEnterprise_D818/bingmaps_3.jpg" style="max-width:350px;max-height:200px;float:left;"/>
			</a>
			<div class="mapdesc">
				<p><a href="http://mapmeld.appspot.com/bingtest.html" target="_blank">Bing Maps Example</a> by olpcMAP</p>
				<p>This is a starter example of olpcMAP's open KML data used with a mapping service.</p>
				<p>How does Bing Maps look?  Try the Birds Eye view in Boston</p>
				<p>A similar <a href="http://mapmeld.appspot.com/kickstart-google.html" target="_blank">Google Kickstart Map</a> is a quick starting point for using olpcMAP API with Google Maps.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<br/>
		<h4>Social Toolbar Example</h4>
		<div>
			<a href="http://mapmeld.appspot.com/socialtest.html" target="_blank">
				<img src="http://cdn.wibiya.com/Graphics_Website/hp/page1_image.jpg" style="max-width:350px;max-height:200px;float:left;"/>
			</a>
			<div class="mapdesc">
				<p><a href="http://mapmeld.appspot.com/socialtest.html" target="_blank">Social Toolbar Example</a> by olpcMAP</p>
				<p>Try olpcMAP with the social networking toolbar from Wibiya.com.</p>
				<p>Should this be on olpcMAP.net?  Let us know.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<br/>
		<h4>Tagging Example</h4>
		<div>
			<a href="http://mapmeld.appspot.com/tags-test.html" target="_blank">
				<img src="http://stanford2009.wikispaces.com/file/view/tagcloud.gif/74680017/tagcloud.gif" style="max-width:350px;max-height:200px;float:left;"/>
			</a>
			<div class="mapdesc">
				<p><a href="http://mapmeld.appspot.com/tags-test.html" target="_blank">Tagging Example</a> by olpcMAP</p>
				<p>Try olpcMAP with several different automatically-added tags connected to search.</p>
				<p>Should this be on olpcMAP.net?  Let us know.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div id="coverwindow" style="display:none;position:fixed;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;top:100px;border:1px solid black;font-size:16pt;text-align:right;background-color:#333333;">
		<input type="button" value="X" style="border:1px solid black;color:black;font-size:16pt;" onclick="closeCoverWindow();"/>
		<br/>
		<form id="signinform" style="width:100%;background-color:#ffffff; text-align:left; font-size:13pt;" action="http://mapmeld.appspot.com/olpcMAP/contact?id=you" method="POST">
			E-mail <input id="emaillogin" name="login"/><br/>
			<!--Password <input id="passwordlogin" type="password" name="password"/><hr/>-->
			Message<br/><textarea name="message" width="300"></textarea>
			<input type="submit" style="width:50%;text-align:center;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;" value="Send"/>
		</form>
		<div id="infoform"></div>
	</div>
</body>
</html>